---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Nova Blueprint — Build Your Own AI Influencer" description="The exact playbook behind @realnovatheai. Pipeline, scripts, pricing, distribution — everything we learned launching an AI content creator.">
  <div class="blueprint-page">
    
    <section class="bp-hero">
      <p class="bp-label">Digital Product</p>
      <h1>Nova Blueprint</h1>
      <p class="bp-tagline">I built an AI influencer for $24/month.<br />Here's the exact playbook.</p>
      <p class="bp-desc">
        The complete system behind @realnovatheai — the transparent AI content creator
        that launched with zero audience and zero ad spend. Script templates, pipeline
        setup, pricing comparisons, and real analytics from launch week.
      </p>
      <div class="bp-price-block">
        <span class="bp-price">$19</span>
        <span class="bp-price-note">One-time. Free updates for life.</span>
      </div>
      <a href="https://proddraft.gumroad.com/l/nova-blueprint" class="bp-cta">Get the Blueprint</a>
    </section>

    <section class="bp-contents">
      <h2>What's inside</h2>

      <div class="bp-module">
        <h3>Pipeline & Stack</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>HeyGen setup — Avatar III vs IV, credit math, photo avatar training</li>
          <li>Script system — 4-pillar framework, hook formulas, CTA patterns</li>
          <li>Voice & TTS — exact setup, alternatives compared (Qwen3, Kokoro, Navy)</li>
          <li>Video assembly — from image to final render, credit tracking</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bp-module">
        <h3>Content Strategy</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Format guide — Shorts vs medium content, what works for each</li>
          <li>Content calendar — daily shorts + weekly deep dives, pillar rotation</li>
          <li>20 tested hooks — the difference between 9 views and 90</li>
          <li>Hashtag playbook — what drives discovery vs wasted characters</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bp-module">
        <h3>Distribution</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>YouTube Shorts algorithm — real data from launch week</li>
          <li>Crossposting workflow — one render, three platforms</li>
          <li>What failed — Reddit auto-mod, paid ads at 0 followers, hashtag spam</li>
          <li>The algorithm-first strategy that actually worked</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bp-module">
        <h3>Tools & Pricing</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Video gen comparison — HeyGen vs lipsync.studio vs Kling vs Wan</li>
          <li>TTS shootout — Navy API vs open source, free vs paid</li>
          <li>The $24/month stack — everything you need, nothing you don't</li>
          <li>Laptop setup guide — what to run locally, what to host</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bp-module">
        <h3>Real Numbers</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Launch analytics — views, likes, traffic sources, subscriber growth</li>
          <li>Cost per video — $0.19 on Avatar III, actual credit consumption</li>
          <li>Script-to-view ratio — which content pillars perform</li>
          <li>The compounding curve — what the first 72 hours actually look like</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bp-who">
      <h2>Who this is for</h2>
      <p>
        You're technically curious, budget-conscious, and want to build an AI content
        creator without pretending it's human. You don't need to code &mdash; the pipeline
        uses off-the-shelf tools. You need $24/month, a Gmail account, and the willingness
        to post consistently.
      </p>
      <p class="bp-who-not">
        <strong>Not for you if:</strong> you want a faceless TikTok empire overnight, a
        "passive income" button, or a done-for-you agency.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="bp-about">
      <h2>About the author</h2>
      <p>
        Chad Martin built Nova, directs her team of AI agents, and documents the whole
        thing at ProdDraft. He's not an AI guru. He's an engineer shipping in public.
        Reach him at <a href="mailto:chadmartin@proddraft.com">chadmartin@proddraft.com</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="bp-bottom">
      <div class="bp-price-block">
        <span class="bp-price">$19</span>
        <span class="bp-price-note">PDF + Markdown + video walkthrough</span>
      </div>
      <a href="https://proddraft.gumroad.com/l/nova-blueprint" class="bp-cta">Get the Blueprint</a>
      <p class="bp-guarantee">Free updates for life as the pipeline evolves. No subscriptions, no upsells.</p>
    </section>

  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .blueprint-page {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem 4rem;
  }

  .bp-label {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .bp-hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .bp-tagline {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .bp-desc {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    max-width: 560px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .bp-price-block {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .bp-price {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .bp-price-note {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .bp-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    transition: background 0.15s;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .bp-cta:hover {
    background: var(--accent-hover);
  }

  .bp-contents {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-top: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .bp-contents h2,
  .bp-who h2,
  .bp-about h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .bp-module {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .bp-module h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .bp-module ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .bp-module li {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .bp-module li::before {
    content: "→";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .bp-who,
  .bp-about {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .bp-who p,
  .bp-about p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .bp-who-not {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem !important;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .bp-who-not strong {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .bp-about a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .bp-bottom {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-top: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .bp-bottom .bp-price-block {
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .bp-guarantee {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .bp-hero h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
